</p>
<p>
<seg id="20">Tomáš Hanák has written the lyrics of this song and plays the leading role of Jesus in the video clip, where he also sings Xindl X...</seg>
<seg id="21">How did this collaboration?</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id="22">We work together even with other figures from the Czech cultural scene, apart from organizing many charitable events and concerts.</seg>
<seg id="23">We put all our efforts to participate in this project.</seg>
<seg id="24">It has been shown that most of them are interested in and amuses them to work with us.</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id="25">What will be allocated the money raised through the concerts at the end of the world?</seg>
</p>
<p>
